params.812: Reach level 20 in the Strength skill.
params.813: Ensure your combat style is set to provide Strength XP. The Al-Kharid guards in the Al-Kharid palace are suitable targets to fight.
params.814: The Al-Kharid guards in the Al-Kharid palace are suitable targets to fight.|Al-Kharid is to the east of Lumbridge through the toll gate. Remember to take 10 coins to pass through the Al-Kharid gate, you can kill goblins nearby for coins if you forget.|Al-Kharid guards drop a variety of runes and coins.|Al-Kharid guards often attack in groups.|Kebabs are cheap food which can be bought from Karim's kebab shop west of the palace.|There is a bank nearby to the south of Karim's kebab shop.
params.823: You can find Al-Kharid warriors in the Al-Kharid palace court yard.
